#: ../../source/manual/how-tos/two_factor.rst:107
msgid "Step 5 - Test the token"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/manual/how-tos/two_factor.rst:108
msgid ""
"For testing the user authentication, OPNsense offers a simple tester. Go "
"to :menuselection:`System --> Access --> Tester`"
msgstr ""

